COVID vaccines boost your long-term T-cell response, in addition to B-cell/antibody response. So even if youâ€™re deficient in B cells, itâ€™s still worth it to get vaccinated!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An oral antiviral VV116 helped people recover completely from COVID symptoms 2 days faster compared to placebo (11 days vs 13 days). Dr. Griffin says this isnâ€™t as impressive as he would like. VV116 works similarly to remdesivir, and doesnâ€™t have drug-drug interactions like with Paxlovid.&lt;/li&gt;
