&lt;li&gt;From listener q: Loss of taste and smell does not count as a â€œsymptomâ€ when youâ€™re talking about being â€œsymptom-freeâ€ for transmission purposes. There are people out there who still canâ€™t taste or smell a year out....&lt;/li&gt;
