&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://emergency.cdc.gov/cerc/manual/index.asp&quot;&gt;CDCâ€™s Crisis and Emergency Risk Communications (CERC) manual&lt;/a&gt; (also see &lt;a href=&quot;/talk/content-design-center-stage/&quot;&gt;how I applied CERC principles to working with stakeholders&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
