&lt;h2 id=&quot;%E2%80%9Clet%E2%80%99s-wind-the-clocks-back%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D&quot; tabindex=&quot;-1&quot;&gt;â€œLetâ€™s wind the clocks backâ€¦â€&lt;/h2&gt;
