&lt;h2 id=&quot;%E2%80%9Cyou-either-die-a-hero%2C-or-you-live-long-enough-to-see-yourself-become-the-villain%E2%80%9D&quot; tabindex=&quot;-1&quot;&gt;â€œYou either die a hero, or you live long enough to see yourself become the villainâ€&lt;/h2&gt;
