&lt;h2 id=&quot;%E2%80%9Ci-believe-in-harvey-dent%E2%80%9D&quot; tabindex=&quot;-1&quot;&gt;â€œI believe in Harvey Dentâ€&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We all have our own mental models for how the world works. Weâ€™ve meticulously created an architecture of beliefs that govern our reality.&lt;/p&gt;
