&lt;p&gt;We can design around it. Itâ€™s possible. Our mental models are affected by what we perceive as incentives and goals inherent in the system.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To combat the backfire effect, we canâ€™t just burn everything down. We have to replace it with something better. We have to rewrite peopleâ€™s mental models.&lt;/p&gt;
