&lt;p&gt;Take the ARG that started this whole journey. When coming up with a new activity, the foremost thought on the game designersâ€™ minds was player safety. They &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.thrillist.com/entertainment/nation/dark-knight-arg-why-so-serious-alternate-reality-game&quot;&gt;had to predict the extremes of what players might do in their excitement,&lt;/a&gt; and create the activities accordingly.&lt;/p&gt;
