&lt;h2 id=&quot;%E2%80%9Cthe-night-is-darkest-just-before-the-dawn%E2%80%9D&quot; tabindex=&quot;-1&quot;&gt;â€œThe night is darkest just before the dawnâ€&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I believe we can do it. When creating a new community culture, we may not know whatâ€™s on the other side. We may only have a set of principles to guide our way. But thatâ€™s part of the beauty â€“ by working with what we have, we can come up with something even better than we could imagine.&lt;/p&gt;
