&lt;p&gt;Stop worrying about the degrees you donâ€™t have. Stop worrying how â€œgoodâ€ at design you are. Stop worrying about getting the attention of so-and-so famous designer or someone at this-and-this famous company. Stop worrying if youâ€™ll measure up, if someone will just give you a chance to do design.&lt;/p&gt;
