&lt;h2 id=&quot;personas&quot; tabindex=&quot;-1&quot;&gt;Personas&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After assigning these two values, and noting that there was a general match between the two qualities, I came up with 4 personas:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;â€œTrailblazerâ€ â€“ mostly spearheads artistic direction, expects others to work on them. Primarily staff members, some curators. hitRECord is their primary daily activity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;â€œCollaboratorâ€ â€“ mostly works on active projects, fulfilling specific requests. Likely has production job in a creative industry or has serious artistic hobby, uses hitRECord as artistic outlet.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;â€œSpongeâ€ â€“ mostly contributes to ongoing collaborations, but doesnâ€™t aim for active projects or requests. Often has completely non-creative job, uses hitRECord as artistic outlet&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;â€œArchiverâ€ â€“ mostly uploads own work without paying attention to other collaborations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
